PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778324573
OL,3,CNew mum cuddles hours-old baby monkey
OL,4,Cstill with umbilical cord attached
OL,6,FThe team at the park is thrilled with
OL,7,Fthe new arrivals as fewer than 8,000
OL,8,FBarbary macaques are thought to remain
OL,9,Fin the wild.
OL,11,FThey will be monitoring the progress
OL,12,Fof the first new arrival and its mum,
OL,13,Fand delayed announcing its arrival, as
OL,14,Fmum is said to be "inexperienced".
OL,16,F140 Barbary macaque monkeys live in
OL,17,Fthe Staffordshire woodland where they
OL,18,Froam freely and the team try to
OL,19,Fpreserve the behaviours they would
OL,20,Fhave in the wild.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
