OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778324573
OL,3,CNew mum cuddles hours-old baby monkey
OL,4,Cstill with umbilical cord attached
OL,6,FPark Director Matt Lovatt said,
OL,8,F"Baby season is an incredible time of
OL,9,Fyear, as the little ones are extremely
OL,10,Fpopular, not just among excited
OL,11,Fvisitors but for the monkeys also.
OL,13,F"Baby Barbary macaques have many
OL,14,F'babysitters' with many males taking
OL,15,Fan active role in caring for the
OL,16,Fsmallest members of the group, a
OL,17,Fcharacteristic rare amongst primates.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
