PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778324573
OL,3,CNew mum cuddles hours-old baby monkey
OL,4,Cstill with umbilical cord attached
OL,6,F"We're thrilled that baby season has
OL,7,Fbegun. We hope to see between 6-10
OL,8,Fbirths each year, the new arrivals
OL,9,Fwill be looked after by their fellow
OL,10,Fgroup members and start learning the
OL,11,Ffascinating Barbary macaque way of
OL,12,Flife from the very first day of their
OL,13,Flives due to the incredible
OL,14,Fenvironment of which they live.
OL,16,FWe can't wait to see who's next to be
OL,17,Fwelcomed into the world, as we expect
OL,18,Fmore babies to arrive very soon"
OL,26,@zD@`O]
